# This app has NO build-time (`$env/static/*`) or client env vars.
#
# Kudi's WhatsApp number lives in wrangler.jsonc `vars` as WA_NUMBER and is read
# at runtime via platform.env (src/lib/server/db.ts → getWaNumber). In local dev
# the Cloudflare platform proxy serves it from wrangler.jsonc automatically, so
# there's nothing to copy here.
#
# Local-only secrets/toggles (e.g. ADMIN_DEV for the /admin bypass) go in
# `.dev.vars`, not here. See docs/DEPLOY.md.
#
# The wa.me prefilled message is hardcoded in src/lib/wa.ts (WA_PREFILL) because
# it must exactly match the bot's flow trigger.
